<br>
Tiffeater, why don't you provide a log or two to substantiate your claims.  What I DID say (After getting beaten on repeatedly the first few pulls) was that SK's and Paladins have an easier time holding aggro than Warriors, AND that it was unfair to Warriors.<br>
<br>
I also said that it wasn't (for the most part) Warriors fault, that due to changes made by Sony, they (Warriors) are having more difficulty it seems.<br>
<br>
Anyone who's played this game for more than a month or so understands how Warriors (especially) are tied to their equipment. Spells however, (For the most part) are available at a vendor, and certainly the Stun line (Paladin) and Darkness line (SK) aren't that hard to come by. <br>
<br>
I also provided anecdotal evidence and mentioned that earlier in PoD a 54 Paladin had an easier time holding aggro than a 61 Warrior.<br>
<br>
But hey, don't believe me, go over to the Steelwarrior website and do a search on holding aggro. (<!--EZCODE AUTOLINK START--><a href="http://www.thesteelwarrior.org/forum/search.php?s=0a5801a897205eb19e19aa16ea572401&action=showresults&searchid=27724&sortby=lastpost&sortorder=descending)">www.thesteelwarrior.org/f...escending)</a><!--EZCODE AUTOLINK END--><br>
<br>
FIVE pages come up.<br>
<br>
For what it's worth you may be a great taunter. You certainly didn't show it that day, and insofar as the tanks I have grouped with since then you rank in the lower half.<br>
<br>
But keep on deluding yourself that 2 x 1HS and your taunt button &gt; Spells.<br>
<br>
I'm also trying to figure out the logic behind the premise that because you're unguilded you're a subpar player.  This is especially odd, because you yourself were unguilded at the time. <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table> </td></tr></table> <table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top">  Page <a href=http://pub228.ezboard.com/fxevserverboardsfrm6.showMessageRange?topicID=893.topic&start=1&stop=20>1</a><a href=http://pub228.ezboard.com/fxevserverboardsfrm6.showMessageRange?topicID=893.topic&start=21&stop=40>2</a> <b>3</b>  </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub228.ezboard.com/fxevserverboardsfrm6.showPrevMessage?topicID=893.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub228.ezboard.com/fxevserverboardsfrm6.showNextMessage?topicID=893.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a self href=http://pub228.ezboard.com/fxevserverboardsfrm6.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=893.topic&index=41><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/traditional/addReply.jpg border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub228.ezboard.com/fxevserverboardsfrm6.emailToFriend?topicID=893.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub228.ezboard.com/fxevserverboardsfrm6.threadControl?topicID=893.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/traditional/deleteThread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands</a><br> <a href=http://pub228.ezboard.com/fxevserverboardsfrm6.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=893.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/ultimate/subscribe.gif width=20 height=20 border=0 alt="Click to receive email notification of replies"> Click to receive email notification of replies</a> <br>  <a href=http://pub228.ezboard.com/fxevserverboardsfrm6.unsubscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=893.topic>